rules.string: IF (cp != {asympt} OR oldpeak <= 0.50) AND chol <= 327.50 AND (fbs = {t} OR sex = {female}) AND (age >= 36.50 OR sex = {female}) AND thalach >= 104.00 THEN class = <50

IF (cp = {asympt} OR oldpeak >= 2.50) AND (oldpeak >= 0.55 OR ca >= 0.50 OR age <= 40.50) AND (trestbps >= 110.00 OR exang = {yes} OR sex = {male}) AND (thalach <= 170.50 OR trestbps <= 139.00) AND (cp = {asympt} OR exang = {yes}) AND (trestbps >= 109.00 OR fbs = {f}) AND (thalach <= 158.50 OR ca >= 2.00 OR thal = {reversable_defect}) AND (chol <= 373.50 OR thal = {reversable_defect}) AND (age <= 70.50 OR sex = {male}) THEN class = >50_1
IF cp != {asympt} AND (oldpeak <= 2.65 OR slope = {down}) AND chol <= 327.50 AND (thalach >= 109.50 OR fbs = {t}) AND (age >= 36.50 OR sex = {female}) THEN class = <50
IF (thal = {reversable_defect} AND thalach <= 143.00 AND oldpeak >= 0.05) OR (restecg = {st_t_wave_abnormality} AND cp = {asympt}) OR (slope = {down} AND cp = {asympt}) THEN class = >50_1
IF thal = {normal} AND oldpeak <= 2.65 AND (sex = {female} OR restecg = {normal}) AND chol <= 327.50 AND (thalach >= 104.00 OR fbs = {t}) THEN class = <50

IF (thal != {normal} OR oldpeak >= 2.50 OR thalach <= 111.00) AND (oldpeak >= 0.55 OR restecg = {left_vent_hyper} OR trestbps <= 104.00) AND (cp != {typ_angina} OR age <= 39.50 OR trestbps <= 110.00) AND (oldpeak >= 0.05 OR thal = {normal} OR chol >= 228.50) AND (age <= 65.50 OR thalach <= 126.00) THEN class = >50_1

IF (thalach >= 169.50 AND slope = {up} AND oldpeak <= 1.50) OR (cp = {atyp_angina} AND oldpeak = ca) OR (cp = {non_anginal} AND sex = {female} AND trestbps < thalach) OR (restecg = {st_t_wave_abnormality} AND exang = {no}) OR chol < thalach OR (cp = {atyp_angina} AND fbs = {t}) OR (chol >= 346.50 AND thal = {normal}) OR (cp = {atyp_angina} AND trestbps >= 132.00) OR (cp = {typ_angina} AND fbs = {t} AND oldpeak <= 1.20) OR (cp = {non_anginal} AND age <= 54.50) THEN class = <50

IF slope != {up} AND thalach <= 176.00 AND trestbps >= 108.00 AND age <= 70.50 AND (cp != {atyp_angina} OR thalach >= 153.50) AND (cp != {typ_angina} OR chol >= 271.50) AND (thal != {normal} OR age >= 55.00) AND chol <= 486.50 THEN class = >50_1

IF (oldpeak <= 0.50 AND chol <= 269.00 AND ca <= 0.00) OR (cp != {asympt} AND slope = {up} AND age <= 57.00) OR (trestbps <= 108.00 AND thalach <= 152.00) OR (chol >= 339.00 AND cp = {non_anginal}) OR (trestbps <= 108.00 AND sex = {male}) OR (cp = {typ_angina} AND sex = {female}) OR (cp = {atyp_angina} AND trestbps >= 132.00 AND fbs = {f}) OR (cp = {typ_angina} AND chol <= 242.00 AND exang = {no}) THEN class = <50

IF (thalach <= 160.00 AND age <= 65.50 AND chol >= 228.50) OR (oldpeak >= 2.00 AND chol <= 234.00 AND age <= 64.00) OR (ca >= 2.00 AND cp = {asympt}) OR (slope = {down} AND sex = {male}) OR (chol >= 325.50 AND restecg = {left_vent_hyper}) OR (thalach <= 120.00 AND ca >= 0.50) THEN class = >50_1
